{"image_id": "CINF_2013_page_82", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Cincinnati Financial Corporation - 2013 10-K - Page 80", "bbox": [435.0, 1566.8, 839.8, 1585.4]}, {"text": "Beginning in March of 2014, commission rates for selected personal lines insurance products will be modified,", "bbox": [104.2, 85.8, 1120.8, 109.1]}, {"text": "resulting in an estimated reduction in our personal lines total underwriting expense ratio, on a full-year basis, of", "bbox": [104.2, 110.8, 1130.1, 134.1]}, {"text": "approximately 2 percentage points.", "bbox": [104.2, 135.8, 434.2, 159.1]}, {"text": "Personal Lines of Business Analysis", "bbox": [104.2, 185.8, 466.9, 209.1]}, {"text": "We prefer to write personal lines coverages within accounts that include both auto and homeowner coverages as", "bbox": [104.2, 219.2, 1148.2, 242.4]}, {"text": "well as coverages from the other personal business line. As a result, we believe that the personal lines segment is", "bbox": [104.2, 244.2, 1157.9, 267.4]}, {"text": "best measured and evaluated on a segment basis. However, we provide line-of-business data to analyze growth", "bbox": [104.2, 269.2, 1142.9, 292.4]}, {"text": "and profitability trends separately for each line. The accident year loss data provides current estimates of incurred", "bbox": [104.2, 294.2, 1155.2, 317.4]}, {"text": "loss and loss expenses and corresponding ratios over the most recent three accident years. Accident year data", "bbox": [104.2, 319.2, 1132.5, 342.4]}, {"text": "classifies losses according to the year in which the corresponding loss events occur, regardless of when the losses", "bbox": [104.2, 344.2, 1166.0, 367.4]}, {"text": "are actually reported, recorded or paid.", "bbox": [104.2, 369.2, 463.1, 392.4]}, {"text": "For 2013, our personal auto line of business had a total loss and loss expense ratio significantly higher than", "bbox": [104.2, 419.2, 1100.0, 442.4]}, {"text": "desired. As discussed in the overview section of Personal Lines Insurance Results of Operations, and below, we", "bbox": [104.2, 444.2, 1141.8, 467.4]}, {"text": "are taking actions to improve pricing and reduce loss costs that we expect to benefit future profitability trends. A", "bbox": [104.2, 469.2, 1133.7, 492.4]}, {"text": "similar approach was used to improve the total loss and loss expense ratio for our homeowner line of business to a", "bbox": [104.2, 494.2, 1167.1, 517.4]}, {"text": "satisfactory result for 2013.", "bbox": [104.2, 519.2, 354.3, 542.4]}, {"text": "Personal Auto", "bbox": [104.2, 569.2, 244.6, 592.4]}, {"text": "(Dollars in millions)", "bbox": [110.4, 615.4, 246.5, 633.8]}, {"text": "Years ended December 31,", "bbox": [648.6, 611.0, 874.3, 634.0]}, {"text": "2013-2012", "bbox": [944.4, 610.8, 1034.6, 633.8]}, {"text": "2012-2011", "bbox": [1065.6, 611.0, 1155.9, 634.0]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [627.1, 639.9, 668.8, 663.0]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [739.6, 640.1, 781.2, 663.2]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [852.4, 640.1, 894.1, 663.2]}, {"text": "Change %", "bbox": [942.4, 639.9, 1036.7, 663.0]}, {"text": "Change %", "bbox": [1067.3, 640.1, 1153.5, 663.2]}, {"text": "Written premiums", "bbox": [110.4, 669.3, 262.6, 692.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [602.1, 669.1, 612.5, 692.1]}, {"text": "460", "bbox": [647.9, 669.1, 679.2, 692.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [714.6, 669.3, 725.0, 692.4]}, {"text": "425", "bbox": [763.9, 669.3, 795.1, 692.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [827.1, 669.3, 837.5, 692.4]}, {"text": "385", "bbox": [876.4, 669.3, 907.6, 692.4]}, {"text": "8", "bbox": [1028.4, 669.1, 1038.9, 692.1]}, {"text": "10", "bbox": [1138.9, 669.3, 1159.7, 692.4]}, {"text": "Earned premiums", "bbox": [110.4, 698.5, 258.0, 721.5]}, {"text": "443", "bbox": [647.9, 698.3, 679.2, 721.3]}, {"text": "404", "bbox": [763.9, 698.5, 795.1, 721.5]}, {"text": "368", "bbox": [876.4, 698.5, 907.6, 721.5]}, {"text": "10", "bbox": [1018.0, 698.3, 1038.9, 721.3]}, {"text": "10", "bbox": [1138.9, 698.5, 1159.7, 721.5]}, {"text": "Loss an